      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan documented with version control, regression testing, and code review records meeting MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Version control and basic regression testing are in place, but formal SQA plan does not meet the depth required for MRL 5. Code review records are incomplete for the hemolysis sub-model routines."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
