      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error quantified for all operating points; solver error shown to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error was not assessed. Residual convergence plots were provided but no formal quantification of iterative or round-off error was performed. Flagged as an epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
