      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo propagation results linked to credibility evidence.",
      "rationale": "While Monte Carlo UQ was performed as part of the analysis workflow, the formal credibility factor assessment for model inputs was not completed. Input parameter distributions were not documented with traceability to clinical or material data sources."
    },
