      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test samples used in validation experiments must be characterized and shown representative of the clinical population including variability in blood rheology.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization was not assessed. Experimental data used bovine blood without characterization of inter-sample variability. No mapping to human blood rheological variability was provided."
